Package com.google.openbidder.bidding.json Description

JSON serialization support for the Open Bidder-specific OpenRTB extensions. These extensions are used only internally by the Open Bidder framework, they're not designed to be sent to any exchange; but the full JSON serialization including all extensions may be useful for logging or other purposes. See OpenRtbJsonReader for a bigger sample of how to writer readers for more complex objects, arrays, etc.
